description:
SimeonOnSecurity (SOS) is a progressive web application (PWA) dedicated to providing valuable insights and information in the realm of security and automation. Our goal is to offer unique and in-depth technical content that goes beyond the surface level information typically found online. With a focus on cybersecurity and privacy, we aim to empower our readers with the knowledge they need to navigate this dynamic field effectively.

Led by Simeon, a highly skilled Systems Administrator, SOS brings together a wealth of technical expertise and a passion for the industry. Simeon's commitment to cybersecurity and privacy extends beyond his professional role, as he embraces his identity as a tinkerer, hobbyist, and self-proclaimed geek and nerd. Drawing from a history of technical proficiency that dates back to his early years, Simeon's journey began at the age of 12, troubleshooting and resolving issues on a laptop that struggled to run Windows XP smoothly.

Today, Simeon maintains a cutting-edge data center and lab at home, showcasing his unwavering dedication to the field. With computing and storage capabilities that rival many small businesses, SOS serves as a platform to share Simeon's expertise and passion for security and automation.

Explore SimeonOnSecurity to delve into the inner workings of the cybersecurity world, discover insightful articles, and stay updated on the latest advancements. Embrace our PWA as your go-to resource for comprehensive information and practical guidance on all things security and automation.
